# Shell Scripting

Ex-1:

[cloudshell-user@ip-10-0-171-90 Effective]$ cat -n function.sh 
     1  #!/bin/bash
     2
     3  echo -n "Enter a no: "
     4  read x
     5
     6  echo -n "Enter a new no: "
     7  read y
     8
     9  echo "Sum of x & y is: $((x+y))"
    10
[cloudshell-user@ip-10-0-171-90 Effective]$ ./function.sh 
Enter a no: 10
Enter a new no: 20
Sum of x & y is: 30
[cloudshell-user@ip-10-0-171-90 Effective]$ 

Ex-2:

[cloudshell-user@ip-10-0-171-90 Effective]$ cat -n function.sh 
     1  #!/bin/bash
     2
     3  # Create a function
     4
     5  function Add()
     6  {
     7  echo -n "Enter a no: "
     8  read x
     9
    10  echo -n "Enter a new no: "
    11  read y
    12
    13  echo "Sum of x & y is: $((x+y))"
    14  }
    15
    16  # Call a function
    17  Add
    18
[cloudshell-user@ip-10-0-171-90 Effective]$ 
[cloudshell-user@ip-10-0-171-90 Effective]$ ./function.sh 
Enter a no: 10
Enter a new no: 20
Sum of x & y is: 30
[cloudshell-user@ip-10-0-171-90 Effective]$ 


